snippet.title: Zyger
snippet.description:
Hey , my name is Zyger I'm a 19 year old student and I make games and program. (When I'm not lazy) I'm currently working on a game called Project Jude and creating devlog videos of the making process. I also make other game development related videos that I suggest you check out. Anyways hope you enjoy my content and i hope you have a good day or night depending on when or if your reading this. 
That's it bye :')
